00:48:31,880 --> 00:48:57,445
And I think it's a combination of city staff, homeowners, tenants, and tenants in that protected class, all members of Somerville, sorry, residents of Somerville. That's kind of the formulation. Do we want to see, talk about going that route, or should we talk about tasking an existing department or board with these responsibilities?

